===Personality===
*Hiburi, unlike her sister [[Daitou]], is more reserved and softspoken.
*She refers to herself in third person.
*In her Secretary 3 line, she can be heard telling [[Daitou]] to stop messing around, which suggests that she has to look after Daitou.

