==Trivia==
*Named after Hiburi Island located near Uwajima, Ehime.
*Launched in April 1944, she was the first of her class and a combination design of the preceeding Mikura Class and designs for the later Ukuru class.
*She led a very short service life, being sunk by USS Harder (along with Matsuwa and Sado) in August '44 as part of the ill fated HI-71 convoy.

